{"tid":1022472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧華馬斯：山齊士對阿仙奴好重要 該選擇重返","createTime":"2019-02-15T05:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T05:36:26.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59a387c7d672a35d47401ec42e5eb847e86884bf","tid":1022472,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"　近日，前阿仙奴翼鋒奧華馬斯接受採訪表示，轉會到曼聯的山齊士可以重新回到阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n　　奧華馬斯說道：「我非常尊重山齊士，因為他在阿仙奴時做得非常好，我不知道他的離開是否是一個好的決定。」<br />\n　　「這類球員對阿仙奴來說非常重要，在山齊士之後，阿仙奴試圖簽下另一名這樣的球員，但他們並沒有找到，所以山齊士可以回到阿仙奴。」"},{"pid":"c8c0b4e35473bc5ee0a9033e36091b983b91a6f1","tid":1022472,"uid":23655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀<br />\n玩鳩我地定玩鳩曼聯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2a85a6cceb27868d6ddb4bc2c7558e8d3e42e8","tid":1022472,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"爺爺最重要"},{"pid":"926950deb67011a7816f1d1003897319fe6169b6","tid":1022472,"uid":171901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"佢同廠好大仇口"},{"pid":"094438fb0dcd3fc1dd1c49b915421a0dad645351","tid":1022472,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪收左全能到仆街錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc693055a35c4f4fa9edd8bf168946928d1f221","tid":1022472,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1022449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1022449/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔小心開2個,去果邊傾"}]}